    <item>
      <title>华尔街预计美元将进一步上涨，但对涨幅存在分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/dollar-s-trump-fueled-rally-unites-wall-street-on-bullish-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 威胁征收全面关税，美元的涨势正在增强，货币策略师们一致认为美元还有进一步上涨的空间，同时也在博弈美元能上涨多少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/dollar-s-trump-fueled-rally-unites-wall-street-on-bullish-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 16:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>劳资纠纷阻碍贸易，加拿大下令港口重启</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/canada-orders-ports-to-restart-as-labor-disputes-choke-trade-m3elw67s</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的政府指示一个独立劳工委员会结束加拿大最大港口的停工，就像 8 月份对铁路部门采取的停工措施一样，以阻止该国经济陷入混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/canada-orders-ports-to-restart-as-labor-disputes-choke-trade-m3elw67s</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 15:27:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
